```java
import java.util.stream.IntStream;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int maxValue = 10;
        IntStream.rangeClosed(1, maxValue)
                .filter(i -> i > maxValue / 2)
                .forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}
```

In this code:

